data.description: This beautiful 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath home is a golfer's dream, with the golf course just two blocks away in a highly sought-after neighborhood. The home boasts original hardwood flooring on the main level, with a finished basement that has a separate entrance providing rental opportunities. The basement also offers ample storage space, including a shop area, and a large bonus room with potential to be a playroom or gaming room. Enjoy the scenic views from the lovely decking in both the front and back of the house. Benefit from a double garage and additional off-street parking, with a large, low maintenance lot. Don't miss out!
